<para>
  The desktop product has been discontinued. &slea;&nbsp;16 is available with a minimal desktop
  environment based on GNOME 48, including essential applications such as the Firefox web browser, file browser, viewers for PDFs and images, and so on.
</para>
<para>
  Changes in desktop technologies:
</para>
<itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
    <para>
      X11 is no longer shipped, therefore, desktop sessions use Wayland.
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
      VNC server in no longer VNC shipped. Remote desktop and sharing is provided using RDP.
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
      <literal>gtk2, Qt5, wxWidgets</literal> widget libraries were dropped.
    </para>
  </listitem>
</itemizedlist>
